title: Christian Atsu again left out of Bournemouth team against Tottenham Hotspur
text:
15:10 CET Christian Atsu again left out of Bournemouth team against Tottenham Hotspur - www.ghanasoccernet.com Ghana and Bournemouth winger Christian Atsu in action 
Ghana winger Christian Atsu's wait for a premier league game continues as he has been left out of the Bournemouth team that will face Tottenham Hotspur this afternoon. 
Atsu who joined Bournemouth from fellow premier league side Everton is yet to make an entrance for Bournemouth in the league this season. 
For more Ghana football news visit www.ghanasoccernet.com
